37
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:13,239
But we kick off by talking
about this, the humble

38
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,959
pick-up truck. Fred!

39
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,319
Say some words.

40
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,439
I will do that.

41
00:03:17,440 --> 00:03:19,199
Pick-ups are on the rise here
in the UK,

42
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:21,199
but pretty much everywhere
else on the planet

43
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:22,759
they're already massive news.

44
